metadata.name: INSIDES
metadata.description:
INSIDES 
A free music NFT for all Shxdw collectors 

Vox + Lyrics by Shxdw 
Production by Grl 
Mixed + Mastered by Jana 
Album Art by Nilus 

Lyrics: 

(Verse 1) 2x
I met him at a party 
Met him at a party 
But I 
Couldn’t tell you what he was wearing 

I’ve gouged out my eyes 
I’ve gouged out my eyes 
I've got no buisness staring 

(Verse 2) 2x
I have come to the conclusion that my insides 
Don’t belong outside 
(I don’t belong here, I don’t belong anywhere)
Don’t belong outside 

With you 10x

(Verse 3)
I met him at a party 
Met him at a party 
But I 
Couldn’t tell you what I was wearing 

He put his lips 
up  against my lips 
My god, 
I finally felt some kind of heaven 

(Verse 4) 2x
I wish there was a warning sign 
That came with my fucked up mind 
I would never put you inside me
